ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2015-16
PrecisAppointment of DEBORAH CHATSIS as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guatemala, and as High Commissioner for Canada in Belize, with residence in Guatemala City; SANDRA MCCARDELL as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of South Africa, and as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria; PATRICIA MCCULLAGH as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Côte d’Ivoire; and MARIANICK TREMBLAY as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Ecuador.
AttachmentsAttachment
